## API COST MANAGEMENT — CRITICAL

**Prompt caching is MANDATORY on all Anthropic calls.**

### Caching Architecture (v0.9.1 — CONFIRMED WORKING)

The command router uses a two-block system prompt for maximum cache efficiency:

```typescript
system: [
  { type: 'text', text: staticContext, cache_control: { type: 'ephemeral' } },
  { type: 'text', text: staticSystemPrompt, cache_control: { type: 'ephemeral' } },
]
```

- `staticContext` — output of `formatStaticContextForPrompt()` — tags, field knowledge, concept registry
- `staticSystemPrompt` — Karl persona, instructions, action list, JSON format rules, objectSummaries, fieldKnowledge

Dynamic context (task snapshot, pending, date, observations) is prepended to the **last user message**, NOT the system block. This keeps the system block byte-identical between calls so the cache hits.

```typescript
const lastIndex = anthropicMessages.length - 1;
const messagesWithContext = anthropicMessages.map((m, i) => {
  if (i === lastIndex) return { ...m, content: dynamicPrefix + '\n\n---\n\n' + m.content };
  return m;
});
```

**Confirmed cache performance (Apr 24):**
- cache_write: ~9,867 tokens on first message
- cache_read: ~9,867 tokens on subsequent messages
- Savings: ~90% cost reduction on cached tokens

Every fetch to `https://api.anthropic.com/v1/messages` must include:
```typescript
headers: {
  'anthropic-beta': 'prompt-caching-2024-07-31',
},
body: JSON.stringify({
  system: [{ type: 'text', text: systemPrompt, cache_control: { type: 'ephemeral' } }],
  // NOT: system: systemPrompt
})
```

**Token logging — add to every route:**
```typescript
const usage = data.usage;
if (usage) console.log('[route-name] tokens:', {
  input:       usage.input_tokens,
  output:      usage.output_tokens,
  cache_write: usage.cache_creation_input_tokens ?? 0,
  cache_read:  usage.cache_read_input_tokens ?? 0,
});
```

**Current pricing (Sonnet 4, April 2026):**
- Input: $3/million tokens
- Output: $15/million tokens
- Cache write: $3.75/million tokens (1.25x)
- Cache read: $0.30/million tokens (0.1x)

**Routes with caching implemented:**
- `app/api/ko/command/route.ts` ✓
- `app/api/ko/suggest-tags/route.ts` ✓
- `app/api/ko/template/run/route.ts` ✓
- `app/api/ko/template/assist/route.ts` ✓
- `app/api/ko/extract/refine/route.ts` ✓
- `suggestTagsForCapture()` in commandRouter.ts ✓

**Generation model split (v0.8.0):**
- Routing/reasoning: `claude-sonnet-4-20250514`
- Document generation: `claude-haiku-4-5-20251001` — separate rate limit, prevents collision with routing call

