## API ROUTES

```
app/api/ko/session/route.ts          — POST: initialize user workspace on login
app/api/ko/command/route.ts          — POST: classify input, confirm/execute actions (v1.5.1)
app/api/ko/admin/route.ts            — GET/POST/PATCH/DELETE for admin tables
app/api/ko/template/run/route.ts     — POST: unified run endpoint — preview + generate (v0.9.0)
app/api/ko/template/assist/route.ts  — POST: Karl Assist — formatting instructions only (v0.9.0)
app/api/ko/extract/refine/route.ts   — POST: refine extract content
app/api/ko/suggest-tags/route.ts     — POST: tag suggestion (inline + admin modes)
```

