## FILE STRUCTURE

### Pages
```
app/page.tsx                    — root, onAuthStateChange → /workspace or /login
app/login/page.tsx              — Google OAuth sign in
app/workspace/page.tsx          — main workspace shell (v0.9.0)
app/admin/page.tsx              — admin panel (9 tabs, metadata-driven)
app/auth/callback/route.ts      — OAuth callback
```

### Components
```
app/components/KarlSpinner.tsx       — reusable KO reticle spinner
app/components/TagPicker.tsx         — shared tag picker, production hardened
