### Karl Observations Schema
```sql
CREATE TABLE karl_observation (
  observation_id   uuid PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid(),
  user_id          uuid NOT NULL REFERENCES ko_user(id),
  content          text NOT NULL,
  observation_type text, -- 'pattern' | 'preference' | 'flag'
  tags             text[],
  is_active        boolean DEFAULT true,
  created_at       timestamptz DEFAULT now()
);
```
Included in base context bundle (latest ~50). Max 50 active — oldest deactivated on overflow.

